 "lrc": "[00:00.00]We’re in love with the party\n[00:02.56]Party after midnight\n[00:04.16]Smooth like the chords\n[00:05.76]And the low lights\n[00:08.00]808 heartbeat\n[00:09.76]Keeping our souls right\n[00:11.84]We don’t wanna leave\n[00:12.96]We just wanna live the nightlife\n[00:15.68]We’re in love with the party\n[00:18.64]Bodies in the same wave\n[00:20.64]Calm, but the groove\n[00:21.92]Still feels like a heatwave\n[00:24.80]Every little moment\n[00:24.80]That the DJ plays\n[00:26.80]Got us falling deeper\n[00:28.24]In the late-night haze\n[00:30.64]Drums fade out\n[00:32.08]But we still keep swaying\n[00:34.32]Low lights glow\n[00:35.52]While the guitar’s still playing\n[00:37.92]Soft lead hums\n[00:39.36]Like a secret we’re saving\n[00:41.60]Heartbeats sync\n[00:42.96]With the night we’re craving\n[00:45.28]When the snare cuts\n[00:46.24]I can hear your whisper\n[00:48.80]Promise that you’ll stay\n[00:50.24]Till the dawn gets crisper\n[00:52.32]Even when it’s quiet\n[00:53.92]We still feel lifted\n[00:55.92]Party in our souls\n[00:57.52]That’s a lifelong ticket\n[01:00.00]We’re in love with the party\n[01:02.32]Party after midnight\n[01:04.16]Smooth like the chords\n[01:05.76]And the low lights\n[01:08.00]808 heartbeat\n[01:09.76]Keeping our souls right\n[01:11.60]We don’t wanna leave\n[01:12.96]We just wanna live the nightlife\n[01:15.68]We’re in love with the party\n[01:18.64]Bodies in the same wave\n[01:20.64]Calm, but the groove\n[01:21.92]Still feels like a heatwave\n[01:23.68]Every little moment\n[01:24.80]That the DJ plays\n[01:26.80]Got us falling deeper\n[01:28.24]In the late-night haze\n[01:30.72]Drums come back for a second\n[01:32.96]Then they slide away\n[01:34.32]Vinyl crackle holds the memory\n[01:36.64]Of this perfect day\n[01:37.92]Last chord rings\n[01:39.20]While we walk in the city light\n[01:41.36]Still in love with the party\n[01:42.96]Carry it into the night\n[01:44.80]Yeah\n"
